= content_for :hero do
  = image_tag('partner/partnerpage_hero.png')

.container-fluid
  .row-fluid
    .span8.offset2.become-a-partner
      %h1 Become a partner.
      .text
        Together, we can create efficient ways to share business spaces, networks, and resources.
        Desks Near Me helps connect people with excess office space with those seeking space.
        Platform and white-label users can customize the branding, look, and feel of their custom
        marketplace, maintaining the trust associated with their brand and network. The marketplace
        can be public or private, sharing inventory from Desks Near Me or displaying only listings
        created via the platform/white-label marketplace. Desks Near Me platform and white-label options
        allow users to add value to their existing network, and create a new revenue stream that would
        otherwise be lost.

  .row-fluid
    .span10.offset1.partners
      .table
