        .text
          Whether you're a corporation, association, chamber of commerce or agency,
          Desks Near Me offers a partnership that adds significiant value to your
          members or customers while growing your brand globally.

  .row-fluid
    .span10.offset1.extra-money
      .span12
        %h2 Get extra money for your extra space.
        .text
          Do you have unused business spaces that can be shared short term amongst
          trusted networks? Our branded solution gives you the platform to help you
          provide solutions that your members are looking for in their business. If
          you're aiming to generate new revenue streams in all markets internationally
          and provide new value added services, our partnerships can help you quickly
          achieve your goals.
      -#.span6
